name: email-templates
description: Skill dla tworzenia i zarządzania szablonami email (HTML/Plain text) z variable substitution i template inheritance
topics:
  - email
  - templates
  - jinja2
  - html
  - text-formatting
applyTo:
  - path: "**/templates/**"
  - path: "**/email_*.py"
  - path: "**/test_*email*"
languageDetection:
  preferredLanguage: python
  patterns:
    - "template"
    - "email"
    - "html"
